Artist Note: While on the path of life, always take time to listen to the voice in your head, or the feeling in your stomach. Over time this relationship strengthens, and it becomes an extra sense. While creating art, listening to this intuition has helped me to push past boundaries and experiment in ways I had not considered prior.
